---
layout: base.njk
title: ホーム
description: おうちヨガ・ウェルネスで毎日を整える。40〜50代女性のためのリアルな体験ブログ。
---

<style>
  /* ===== ヒーローバナー ===== */
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-dark) 0%, var(--green) 100%);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::after {
    content: '🌿';
    position: absolute;
    right: 1.5rem;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    font-size: 5rem;
    opacity: 0.2;
  }
  .hero-label {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
  .hero p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    opacity: 0.88;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ===== セクションタイトル ===== */
  .section-title {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--green-dark);
    padding: 0.5rem 0 0.5rem 0.8rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--green);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  /* ===== カードグリッド ===== */
  .post-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.2rem;
  }

  .post-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: transform 0.22s, box-shadow 0.22s;
  }
  .post-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
  }

  .post-card-thumb {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-light), #d0ede3);
    height: 150px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .post-card-cat {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0.7rem;
    left: 0.7rem;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: var(--green-dark);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .post-card-body {
    padding: 1.1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    flex: 1;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .post-card-date {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .post-card-title {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text);
    flex: 1;
  }
  .post-card-title a { color: var(--text); }
  .post-card-title a:hover { color: var(--green-dark); }

  .post-card-excerpt {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-sub);
    line-height: 1.6;
    display: -webkit-box;
    -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .post-card-more {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.2rem;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--green-dark);
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
  }
  .post-card-more::after { content: " →"; }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .post-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .hero::after { display: none; }
  }
</style>

<!-- ヒーローバナー -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-label">🌿 おうちウェルネスへようこそ</div>
  <h1>体が硬くても、体調不安でも<br>おうちから始めるヨガ習慣</h1>
  <p>40〜50代女性のリアルな体験談。「できない」を「できた」に変えた記録を届けます。</p>
</div>

<!-- 記事一覧 -->
<div class="section-title">📝 新着記事</div>

<div class="post-grid">
  {% for post in collections.posts %}
  <article class="post-card">
    <div class="post-card-thumb">
      🧘
      <span class="post-card-cat">ヨガ体験談</span>
    </div>
    <div class="post-card-body">
      <div class="post-card-date">{{ post.date | dateJP }}</div>
      <h2 class="post-card-title">
        <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
      </h2>
      {% if post.data.description %}
      <p class="post-card-excerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
      {% endif %}
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-card-more">続きを読む</a>
    </div>
  </article>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
